him and me were in London a while back.

113
00:17:18,973 --> 00:17:20,210
I'm glad to meet you.

307
00:17:21,345 --> 00:17:23,685
I heard a little something through the grapevine.

358
00:17:23,985 --> 00:17:27,408
It hasn't made it into the
papers yet, but you should know.

300
00:17:29,068 --> 00:17:31,764
It seems that Mr. Speedwagon has been murdered.

59
00:17:33,247 --> 00:17:34,923
Are you sure?

355
