Rumor is the cat who did it was some sort of Tibetan monk.

243
00:17:39,413 --> 00:17:42,385
Some sort of monk? Could it be Straizo?

320
00:17:42,901 --> 00:17:45,464
All they're saying is that the bodies of Speedwagon

